@startuml
!theme plain
title Project Coherent Storage - Coherence-CE Data Path
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "vLLM / OpenAI-compatible\nInference Actor" as Actor
component "Coherence-CE Adapter API\n(no OpenZFS/DPU/RDMA/CXL leakage)" as API #D6EAF8
component "Coherence-CE Memory Mesh\nplacement + durability + metrics" as Mesh #D5F5E3
component "GPU HBM / Local DRAM\nKV-D0/D1 active decode" as Hot #F9E79F
component "Host DRAM + governed CXL T1/T1.5\nwarm KV/prefix, metadata, vector heads" as Warm #FCF3CF
component "DPU / SmartNIC Offload\nNVMe-oF + RDMA mediation" as DPU #E8DAEF
component "OpenZFS Mirrored NAND Block Tier\nqualified durability substrate" as ZFS #FADBD8
component "Scheduler Admission\nGREEN / AMBER / RED / DRAIN" as Sched #D7DBDD

Actor --> API : REST / OpenAI-compatible\nor Coherence-native calls
API --> Mesh : actor-scoped operations
Mesh --> Hot : hot KV placement
Mesh --> Warm : warm/recomputable placement
Mesh --> DPU : durable write/read path
DPU --> ZFS : NVMe-oF / RoCEv2 / RDMA
Mesh --> Sched : metrics rollup
Sched --> API : admission / throttling / drain

note bottom of API
Actors know Coherence-CE semantics only.
They do not know CXL devices, vdevs,
RDMA QPs, DPUs, or NVMe namespaces.
end note
@enduml
